summary:
International vision. Affinity with languages. Interest in sales. Cultural awareness. Creative.

Always had an interest in other countries, cultures and languages. I am fluent in English and German and have a reasonable understanding of Spanish. Interested to learn more about international sales. I have a feeling for cultural differences and I like to immerse myself in other cultures. I got a creative mindset and like to think along about new ideas or solutions to certain problems.
